  "HomeWiki": "<div class=\"wikidoc\">\r\n<p><strong>Project Description</strong><br>\r\ncsAnt is a scripting and automation platform originally created for automating builds and related tasks (to replace NAnt).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nInspired by and intended to replace Ant/NAnt, the csAnt utility allows all automation scripts to be written in standard C# code and be executed via cs-script.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nScripts are written in the format of a standard C# console application and can utilize standard C# code and any .NET libraries.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nScripts are compiled and executed on the fly by cs-script. Therefore scripts can be executed immediately after editing them without requiring a manual compilation step.</p>\r\n<h2>Example &quot;Hello World&quot; script</h2>\r\n<div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:blue\">using</span> System;\n<span style=\"color:blue\">using</span> SoftwareMonkeys.csAnt;\n\n<span style=\"color:blue\">class</span> HelloWorldScript : BaseScript\n{\n\t<span style=\"color:blue\">public</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">static</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">void</span> Main(<span style=\"color:blue\">string</span>[] args)\n\t{\n\t\t<span style=\"color:blue\">new</span> HelloWorldScript().Start(args);\n\t}\n\t\n\t<span style=\"color:blue\">public</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">override</span> <span style=\"color:blue\">bool</span> Run(<span style=\"color:blue\">string</span>[] args)\n\t{\n\t\tConsole.WriteLine(<span style=\"color:#a31515\">&quot;Hello world!&quot;</span>);\n\n\t\t<span style=\"color:blue\">return</span> !IsError;\n\t}\n}\n</pre>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Getting Set Up</h2>\r\n<p>To set up csAnt ready for a build or for use, run the setup script...<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Linux:</strong><br>\r\n<em>sh csAnt-setup.sh</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Windows:</strong><br>\r\n<em>cscript csAnt-setup.vbs</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nThis will download the library files required to run.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<h2>Execution</h2>\r\n<p>To execute csAnt scripts use the following commands:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Linux:</strong><br>\r\n<em>sh csAnt.sh HelloWorld</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Windows:</strong><br>\r\n<em>csAnt.bat HelloWorld</em></p>\r\n<h2>Output</h2>\r\n<div style=\"color:black; background-color:white\">\r\n<pre><span style=\"color:gray\">/</span><span style=\"color:gray\">/</span> <span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span>\n<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span><span style=\"color:gray\">/</span> Executing script: HelloWorld\n<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span><span style=\"color:gray\">/</span> Directory: <span style=\"color:gray\">/</span>home<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span>user<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span>Projects<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span>SoftwareMonkeys<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span>csAnt\n\nHello world!\n\n<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span><span style=\"color:gray\">/</span> Finished executing script: HelloWorld\n<span style=\"color:gray\">/</span><span style=\"color:gray\">/</span> <span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span style=\"color:gray\">--</span><span 